**Sea Fort RPA AI** is an AI-powered enterprise RPA (Robotic Process Automation) desktop suite developed to automate HR and OHS (Occupational Health and Safety) documentation processes.

The system automatically registers personnel data from Excel/CSV files and identifies 11 different mandatory document types (Criminal Records, ID, OHS Instructions, Social Security Entries, etc.) using intelligent OCR and **Filename Dominance (Override)** algorithms, uploading them seamlessly to the Wellcome (OHS) platform.

---

## 🚀 Engine Highlights & Technical Solutions

During development, many chronic issues caused by Selenium and modern web architectures were solved with **hardened architectural shields**:

* **Filename Dominance (AI Override):** To prevent common keywords in document contents (e.g., the "TR Identity No" text on a Criminal Record triggering the ID category) from misleading the AI, a **Filename Dominance** algorithm was implemented. If a keyword is caught in the filename, content scanning is bypassed for 100% accuracy.
* **Stale Element & Ajax Postback Shield:** Element expiration (`StaleElementReferenceException`) during asynchronous Ajax Postback processes on the Wellcome platform is handled with an intelligent retry shield. The system automatically recaptures the freshest DOM element within 0.5 seconds.
* **Typo Synchronization:** Common typos on the platform's dropdown list, such as `"Yapılacak İşen Özgü..."` (instead of "İşe"), were directly integrated into the weight matrix to ensure 10/10 matching quality.
* **Adaptive Turkish Character Handler:** Character encoding issues during case conversion (e.g., `İ -> I`, `Ç -> C`) are standardized via a dedicated pre-processing layer.
* **Advanced Enterprise UI:** A modern control panel built with `CustomTkinter`, supporting dark mode and real-time KPI metrics (Success, Pending, ETA).

